precis:
Authority for the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign an EXCHANGE OF
NOTES amending the AGREEMENT ON AIR TRANSPORT between Canada and the
UNITED MEXICAN STATES, or (b) to issue an Instrument of Full Powers
authorizing either the Hon. Arthur C. Eggleton, the Hon. David Anderson or
Ambassador Marc Perron, to sign the Exchange of Notes.
